The Ooni of Ife, Oba Adeyeye Enitan Ogunwusi, has appealed to youths in the country to be in the vanguard of a better future and shun cultism and internet scam known as Yahoo-Yahoo. He gave the appeal in his palace at Ile-Ife while unveiling the 2021 edition of Royal Young Leadership Forum (RAYLF), a youth development and capacity building programme which he initiated to mentor youths from age 18 to 39. The monarch said the objective was to break the barriers impeding youth development, especially the growth of young starters in the public and private sectors of the country.